{
  "stem": "10829.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And life in those days-- it's hard to believe now, but life in those days were very, very-- oh, it didn't have much meaning.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Surviving was the-- was the agenda, and no matter how-- and that means that if-- if it's-- it's either you or I, and if I have a better chance to survive than you, then so be it.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I'll give you an example.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My uncle, which was a very nice man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He would give you his right hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But there were-- my-- my young brother, and so all he wanted was a drink of water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when you go around for weeks, and we didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were running away from this attack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he kept on-- he was the only one who was crying so much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So my uncle grabbed him and took off his belt and hung him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He still has a mark, my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And my mother grabbed him, took him off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And she actually urinated and she gave him to drink, and he became quiet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And she saved his life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But this is the desperation that I'm trying to bring out that we had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But we were very close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So it was me and my zeyde was pretty much in charge of supplying the food or searching and getting.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Zeyde knew where to get it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He knew all the farms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Day or night, he could sneak into different places, because he lived all his life around there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And me, I was the only one, the strongest, and the only one capable of doing anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My other-- my uncle took-- had to stay take care of the-- of the women and the kids.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my-- my older uncle, he was pretty much shot down.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
